{
  "style": "APA",
  "texts": [
    "Rodrigues et al. (2018) applied transfer learning using CNNs to obtain a feature extractor that can be used for new datasets.",
    "The Kaggle-Plankton dataset was used to train a CNN (source dataset) and an in-house dataset was used as a target dataset to test the suitability of the features.",
    "Orenstein and Beijbom (2017) applied a variety of learning schemes to three very different plankton image datasets.",
    "The bigger labeled image datasets, IFCB and ISIIS, were used to train CNNs both by fine-tuning and from scratch.",
    "Then, the classifiers were used to classify within-domain images directly and as feature extractors for out-of-domain data."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
    "Rodrigues et al. (2018) applied transfer learning using CNNs to obtain a feature extractor that can be used for new datasets.",
    "Orenstein and Beijbom (2017) applied a variety of learning schemes to three very different plankton image datasets."
  ]
}